subject: new J2EEUnit web site !
msgSnippet: J2EEUnit now has a new web site with a different look and more documentation (guides to explain how to install it, use it, configure it, some sample code
messageBody:
J2EEUnit now has a new web site with a different look and more
documentation (guides to explain how to install it, use it, configure
it, some sample code online, a FAQ, ...).

http://j2eeunit.sourceforge.net

Note: J2EEUnit is a framework (based on JUnit) for unit testing
server-side java code.
